        <title>New in Backpack: Page notifications and up-front sharing settings</title>
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/typepad/37signals/products/~3/478752689/new-in-backpack-page-notifications-and-upfront-sharing-settings.html" />
