        <title>[Case Study] Broadband Genie: "You name it, we manage it through Basecamp!"</title>
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/typepad/37signals/products/~3/460004051/broadband-genie.html" />
